To effectively communicate, 
                                    we must realize that we are all different in the way we perceive the world 
                                    and use this understanding as a guide to our communication with others.



~ Anthony Robbins


 



Anthony Robbins, born Anthony J. Mahavoric in California, is a personal empowerment trainer, author, and businessman. He has written several best-selling books including Unlimited Power, Unleash the Power Within and Awaken the Giant Within.



